I"Ä<p><a href="https://www.archlinux.org/">Arch Linux</a> is a lightweight and flexible Linux distribution for x86_64.</p>
<p>Install the needed Python packages.</p>
<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">sudo pacman -S python
sudo pacman -S python-pip</code></pre></figure>
<p>From here on, we recommend you to follow the
